    .container.sm
      p.title About the Project
      p Devoted is a temple app that allows devotee to find nearby temples, learn more about that temple, interact with them give reviews about their experience. Devotees can also become a temple member or a pujari for the temple and people who would like to participate in the day to day activities of the temple can become volunteer. 
      p This app helps users to learn three different aspects i.e Spirituality, Religious and wellness. As of now we would be focusing on the religious part. 


      
    .img-block-long.mb-50
