    .container.sm.mb-40
    
      p.title My Role
      p BI designed this app from the ground up. Working closely with Sridhar (CEO of Virility Solutions Pvt Ltd) to achieve our goals. 
      p Designing this app was a huge challenge due to the time constraints and business objectives. We had a discussion regarding the way we are going to introduce this app in the market. I.e the Platform in which we are going to release the app - Android, iOS or Web. By conducting a thorough brainstorming, we came up with a pretty clear cut numbers in terms of users using a particular platform. 
      p According the stats, we decided to work on the Android app. Our goal was to focus on the overall experience of the user, in this case, the devotees. Since there wasn’t any clear data available on this type of apps, I had to rely on Sridhar to navigate me through the different aspects of the app. 

      .row.align-items-center
