          img.img-fluid(src="assets/img/devotted/challenge.png", alt="")
        .col-md-6
          p.title The Challenge
          p Here the challenge was to integrate traditional job listing with the learning part and the career growth options so that users can choose which career path to take and what to do to achieve it. 

      
      
    .section-breaker.text-center
      p.title Design Strategy
      
    .container.sm
      p.title Understand the Problem and Creating Persona
      p According to Wikipedia, there are 78.9 percent of Indians who follow Hinduism in India. Due to which there are more than 400,000 temples and twice the number of Temple members who take part in the day to day activities in worshipping gods. So we decided to concentrate on one religion first and then add other religions to our app.

      p We also found that people when they visit temple they wear clothes which are usually orange, yellow or white in color. This color combination gave me the idea to choose Orange like gradient as a Primary color combination.

      .img-block
        img.img-fluid(src="assets/img/devotted/persona.png", alt="")
  

      p.sub-title Characters and their pain points:


      p Ramesh is 48 years old, he is a very religious man takes part in the daily activities held at his local temple. He want to be connected to the temple members so that he doesn’t miss any of the programmes. He uses few bhajan apps.


      p Venu Gopal is 18 years old, his father is a pujari at the temple. He also wants to be a pujari one day, so he assists his father in every way possible in the puja and yajna that happens in the temple. He also conducts festivals inside the temple but doesn’t have any efficient way to call his friends and loved once to the festival. As of now he uses apps like facebook and whatsapp to get connected. 

    

      p.title Identifying the User needs
       
      strong DEVOTEES NEEDS
      ul
        li Devotees wanted to quickly navigate through the app.

        li Search Temple easily 
        li Discover various activities that are currently organised by the temple
        li Participate in those activities

        li Connect with the Pujaris or any temple member
        li Know various things like astrology, Daily Mantra or answer quiz questions

        li Would like to receive Healthy tips
  

        
      strong TEMPLE MEMBER NEEDS
      ul
        li Should have access to the temple details

        li Should be able to add or remove any volunteer
        li Invite a Volunteer
        li Chat with other temple members
        li Setup events for the temple 
        li Socialize with devotees and other people in the network

      
